column5: PCG Squeeze is on the way Cant wait to see this fly past 2500 before June 21 calls expire

PCG from Bloomberg One such came late on Wednesday when Bloomberg News reported PGE Corp had proposed a plan to lawmakers in Sacramento for an 11 billion fund to cover claims from previous wildfires and contribute toward covering future ones The plan was reportedly worked up in conjunction with lawyers representing a group of hedge funds holding equity in the bankrupt utilityI say when although curiously PGEs stock had surged well before news of the plan hit the wiresEven they are tacitly acknowledging the criminality in the way this stock is trading

Nailed the PCG short but overstayed my welcome Shorting is short lived most of the time and I disobeyed my own rule That was quite awful We evolve and learn everyday Normally mistakes happen in that brief moment when you think you actually know more than the market Answer you never do
